Fix i18n syntax error and shrink toolbar control buttons

- Fix: Chinese curly quotes in i18n.js broke the JS parser, causing
  the entire i18n module to fail (language switch non-functional).
  Replaced with Unicode escapes (\u201c / \u201d).
- Shrink start/stop buttons to 26x26 player-style icons with clean
  red/green colors and no border.
